column1: Table 6: Top names for baby girls1,2, 2018
1 These rankings have been produced using the exact spelling of the name given at birth registration. Similar names with different spellings have been counted separately.
2 Births where the name was not stated have been excluded from these figures. Of the 319,492 baby girls in the 2018 dataset, 3 were excluded for this reason.
3 Names with a count of 2 or less have been redacted using S40 of the Freedom of Information Act in order to protect the confidentiality of individuals.
